'''布拉酵母菌'''（''Saccharomyces boulardii''），是一種熱帶[[酵母|酵母]]物種，於1923年由法國科學家亨利·布拉德自[[荔枝|荔枝]]與[[山竹|山竹]]中分離出來。在一些[[分類學|分類學]]、[[代謝|代謝]]和遺傳特性上，它與[[釀酒酵母|釀酒酵母]]相近，但略有不同。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Malgoire JY, Bertout S, Renaud F, Bastide JM, Mallié M |title=Typing of Saccharomyces cerevisiae clinical strains by using microsatellite sequence polymorphism |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-microbiology_2005-03_43_3/page/1133 |journal=J. Clin. Microbiol. |volume=43 |issue=3 |pages=1133–7 |year=2005 |pmid=15750073 |doi=10.1128/JCM.43.3.1133-1137.2005 |pmc=1081240}}</ref>布拉酵母菌常用於作為[[益生菌|益生菌]]引入大、小{{link-en|腸粘膜|Human gastrointestinal tract}}，並在宿主防範病原微生物。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Rajkowska|first=Katarzyna|display-authors=etal|title=Probiotic Activity of Saccharomyces cerevisiae var. boulardii Against Human Pathogens|journal=Food Technology and Biotechnology|date=April 2012|volume=50|pages=230–236|url=http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2012/April-June/230.pdf|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309162314/http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2012/April-June/230.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Toma|first=Malda Maija|display-authors=etal|title=Effect of Probiotic Yeast on Genotoxicity|journal=Food Technology and Biotechnology|date=June 2005|volume=43|pages=301–305|url=http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2005/July-September/43-301.pdf|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202083246/http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2005/July-September/43-301.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Soccol|first=Carlos Ricardo|display-authors=etal|title=The Potential of Probiotics: A Review|journal=Food Technology and Biotechnology|date=June 2010|volume=48|pages=413–434|url=http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2010/October-December/ftb_48_413.pdf|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202090201/http://www.ftb.com.hr/images/pdfarticles/2010/October-December/ftb_48_413.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布拉德當年是在觀察到[[東南亞|東南亞]]原住民咀嚼荔枝和山竹表皮以企圖控制[[霍亂|霍亂]]症狀後，首次分離這種酵母。在健康患者，布拉菌已被證實無致病性和非全身性（它維持在胃腸道中，而不會擴散到人體其他部位）。它生長在37℃（98.6°F）。<ref>{{cite journal | title=''Saccharomyces boulardii'': a review of an innovative biotherapeutic agent | author=McFarland L, Bernasconi P | journal=Microb Ecol Health Dis | year=1993 | volume=6 | pages=157–71 | doi=10.3109/08910609309141323 | issue=4}}</ref>

布拉菌在市場上經常以凍乾形式的益生菌銷售，所以常被稱為布拉菌凍乾。

